   <S PAR='128' RSNT='1' SNO='128'>One thing we have to remember is that all adverse circumstances are not real; they are illusions and deceptions from the enemy.</S>
   <S PAR='129' RSNT='1' SNO='129'>AVOIDING PRAYERS THAT ARE NOT PRAYERS</S>
   <S PAR='130' RSNT='1' SNO='130'>If we want to pray properly, there are still other things we have to do.</S>
