   <S PAR='164' RSNT='1' SNO='164'>Many times our prayers are not answered, and we cannot work and do not have the strength because our prayers are foolish, aimless mutterings before God.</S>
   <S PAR='165' RSNT='1' SNO='165'>This is absolutely the trick of Satan.</S>
